fs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Elkanah’s sons: Amasai and Ahimoth,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"his son Elkanah, his son Zophai,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"his son Eliab,"},{"kind":"text","text":" his son Jeroham, and his son Elkanah."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Samuel’s sons: his firstborn Joel, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some LXX mss, Syr, Arabic; other Hb mss omit Joel; 1Sm 8:2"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 8:2","book":"1Sa","chapter":8,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and his second son Abijah."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 8:2","book":"1Sa","chapter":8,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some LXX mss, Syr, Arabic; other Hb mss omit Joel; 1Sm 8:2"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Merari’s sons: Mahli, his son Libni,"},{"kind":"text","text":" his son Shimei, his son Uzzah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"his son Shimea, his son Haggiah,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and his son Asaiah."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These are the men David put in charge of the music in the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s temple "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 15:16–22","book":"1Ch","chapter":15,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 16:4–6","book":"1Ch","chapter":16,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" after the ark came to rest there. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 6:17","book":"2Sa","chapter":6,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 15:25","book":"1Ch","chapter":15,"verse":25,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Ch 15:16–22","book":"1Ch","chapter":15,"verse":16},{"label":"1Ch 16:4–6","book":"1Ch","chapter":16,"verse":4},{"label":"2Sm 6:17","book":"2Sa","chapter":6,"verse":17},{"label":"1Ch 15:25","book":"1Ch","chapter":15,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They ministered with song in front of the tabernacle, the tent of meeting, until Solomon built the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s temple in Jerusalem, and they performed their task according to the regulations given to them. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These are the men who served with their sons."},{"kind":"text","text":" From the Kohathites: Heman the singer,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Joel, son of Samuel,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Elkanah, son of Jeroham,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Eliel, son of Toah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Zuph, son of Elkanah,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Mahath, son of Amasai,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Elkanah, son of Joel,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Azariah, son of Zephaniah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Tahath, son of Assir,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Ebiasaph, son of Korah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Izhar, son of Kohath,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Levi, son of Israel."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Heman’s relative was Asaph, who stood at his right hand:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Asaph son of Berechiah, son of Shimea,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:40","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Michael, son of Baaseiah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:41","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Ethni,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Zerah, son of Adaiah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:42","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Ethan, son of Zimmah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:43","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Jahath,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Gershom, son of Levi."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:44","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the left, their relatives were Merari’s sons:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Ethan son of Kishi, son of Abdi,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:45","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Hashabiah,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Amaziah, son of Hilkiah,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:46","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Amzi, son of Bani,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:47","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"son of Mahli,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Mushi, son of Merari,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Levi."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:48","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Their relatives, the Levites, were assigned to all the service of the tabernacle, God’s temple. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:49","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But Aaron and his sons did all the work of the most holy place. They presented the offerings on the altar of burnt offerings "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 27:1–8","book":"Exo","chapter":27,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and on the altar of incense "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 30:1–7","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to make atonement for Israel according to all that Moses the servant of God had commanded. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 30:10–16","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":10,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 27:1–8","book":"Exo","chapter":27,"verse":1},{"label":"Ex 30:1–7","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":1},{"label":"Ex 30:10–16","book":"Exo","chapter":30,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:50","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 6:4–8","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" are Aaron’s sons: his son Eleazar,"},{"kind":"text","text":" his son Phinehas, his son Abishua,"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Ch 6:4–8","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:51","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"his son Bukki, his son Uzzi,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:52","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"his son Meraioth,"},{"kind":"text","text":" his son Amariah, his son Ahitub,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:53","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"his son Zadok, and his son Ahimaaz."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:54","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These were the places assigned to Aaron’s descendants from the Kohathite family for their settlements in their territory, because the first lot was for them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:4","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:10","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 21:4","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":4},{"label":"Jos 21:10","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:55","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 14:13","book":"Jos","chapter":14,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 15:13","book":"Jos","chapter":15,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" were given Hebron in the land of Judah and its surrounding pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 14:13","book":"Jos","chapter":14,"verse":13},{"label":"Jos 15:13","book":"Jos","chapter":15,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:56","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but the fields and settlements around the city were given to Caleb son of Jephunneh. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:57","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Aaron’s descendants were given: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:13","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:19","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":19,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 21:13","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":13},{"label":"Jos 21:19","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:58","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Hilen "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, LXX; other Hb mss read Hilez"},{"kind":"text","text":" and its pasturelands, Debir and its pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, LXX; other Hb mss read Hilez"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:59","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Ashan and its pasturelands, and Beth-shemesh and its pasturelands. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:60","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From the tribe of Benjamin they were given Geba and its pasturelands, Alemeth and its pasturelands, and Anathoth and its pasturelands. They had thirteen towns in all among their families."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:61","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"To the rest of the Kohathites, ten towns from half the tribe of Manasseh were assigned by lot. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:5","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 6:66–70","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":66,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 21:5","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":5},{"label":"1Ch 6:66–70","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":66}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:62","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The Gershomites were assigned thirteen towns from the tribes of Issachar, Asher, Naphtali, and Manasseh in Bashan according to their families."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:63","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The Merarites were assigned by lot twelve towns from the tribes of Reuben, Gad, and Zebulun according to their families. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:7","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 6:77–81","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":77,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 21:7","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":7},{"label":"1Ch 6:77–81","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":77}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:64","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So the Israelites gave these towns and their pasturelands to the Levites. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:3","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:41","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":41,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 21:3","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":3},{"label":"Jos 21:41","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":41}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:65","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They assigned by lot the towns named above "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 6:57–60","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":57,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the tribes of the descendants of Judah, Simeon, and Benjamin."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Ch 6:57–60","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":57}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:66","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Some "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 21:20–40","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the families of the Kohathites were given towns from the tribe of Ephraim for their territory:"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jos 21:20–40","book":"Jos","chapter":21,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:67","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Shechem (a city of refuge) with its pasturelands in the hill country of Ephraim, Gezer and its pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:68","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Jokmeam and its pasturelands, Beth-horon and its pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:69","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Aijalon and its pasturelands, and Gath-rimmon and its pasturelands. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:70","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From half the tribe of Manasseh, Aner and its pasturelands, and Bileam and its pasturelands were given to the rest of the families of the Kohathites."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:71","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The Gershomites received:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:72","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From the tribe of Issachar they received Kedesh and its pasturelands, Daberath and its pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:73","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Ramoth and its pasturelands, and Anem and its pasturelands. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:74","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From the tribe of Asher they received Mashal and its pasturelands, Abdon and its pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:75","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Hukok and its pasturelands, and Rehob and its pasturelands. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:76","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From the tribe of Naphtali they received Kedesh in Galilee and its pasturelands, Hammon and its pasturelands, and Kiriathaim and its pasturelands."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:77","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The rest of the Merarites received:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:78","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From the tribe of Reuben across the Jordan at Jericho, to the east of the Jordan, they received Bezer in the desert and its pasturelands, Jahzah and its pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:79","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Kedemoth and its pasturelands, and Mephaath and its pasturelands. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:80","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"From the tribe of Gad they received Ramoth in Gilead and its pasturelands, Mahanaim and its pasturelands, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ch:6:81","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Heshbon and its pasturelands, and Jazer and its pasturelands."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279428035}